
= Install / Dependencies

gems 
  haml
  ferret

create the file config/database.yml from the example file config/database.example

rake globalize:setup
rake db:migrate
rake db:fixtures:load


= Notes

The translation interface is at the url : http://localhost:3000/admin/translate
The validation  interface is at the url : http://localhost:3000/jobs/waiting_for_validation

